{"tid":1064454,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 鼻 屎 喻 戀 人","createTime":"2019-03-16T14:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T15:50:27.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b0572f3ff0286644bde9317e9acc8fc2cc57cd75","tid":1064454,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"吳業坤（坤哥）昨日到商台宣傳新歌《和懷念講再見》，坤哥指新歌講述朋友及戀人，這些過客就像鼻垢，令自己呼吸困難，坤哥說：「佢哋好似鼻屎鼻涕咁，擤走就冇咗。」<br />\n<br />\n坤哥邀請了20位歌迷為新歌合唱其中一部份，因為人數眾多，要分四次灌錄，他說：「一啲歌迷好專業，曾參加歌唱比賽。自己做埋其中一個監製，錄歌有男有女，唔係睇樣睇歌藝，另外邀請咗30位歌迷拍MV，有啲返工特登請假過來，有啲係學生。」此外，龔嘉欣笑言被坤哥打爛貞節牌坊，坤哥笑言：「嘉欣可能耳水不平衡乜都講。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190316/large/16ec2p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190316%2Flarge%2F16ec2p7.jpg&h=6cda5ea1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70dd23e05da8d8f8d64955db5ba865201f7215dd","tid":1064454,"uid":65187,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"e5cc5ce074f3e85088c40da3987ac67fc4d4c1bd","tid":1064454,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:24:15.000Z","msg":"aka<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f67f8c7268538fb5c818bfbee7f0c8963c7eebc","tid":1064454,"uid":205645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"照妖鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5f0314134cd7ab05d4fc328de893268e87eae2","tid":1064454,"uid":197644,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.scmedia.com.hk/scm_photos/THREEWEEKLY/201103/126514/684017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmedia.com.hk%2Fscm_photos%2FTHREEWEEKLY%2F201103%2F126514%2F684017.jpg&h=ff66c339&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30359d6c47536d61feb5118333ae